@startuml SystemArchitecture

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam nodesep 15
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam rectangle {
    BorderThickness 2
}

title <b>System Architecture\nBookworms: What is for reading this week? - Full Project Structure
' ══════════════════════════════════════
' PRESENTATION LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**PRESENTATION LAYER** (Blade Views, Tailwind CSS, Public Assets)\n\n**Core Views:** dashboard, explore, leaderboard, progress, assignments, book\n**Auth & Roles:** auth/, admin/, books/, headteacher/teachers/, teacher/classes/, user/show, Site/\n**Layouts:** components/ (layout, login-layout, site-layout, form-inputs...)\n**Public Assets:** images/home/ (wormMovement...), images/pfp/ (cat.png, dog.png...), Logo.png, Placeholder.jpeg\n**Storage:** storage/template/ (authors.txt, student_import_template.csv)" as PRES #B3E5FC

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' ROUTING LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**ROUTING LAYER**\n<i>routes/web.php</i>  |  <i>routes/console.php</i>\nMaps URL endpoints to Controllers" as ROUTES #C8E6C9

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' MIDDLEWARE LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**MIDDLEWARE LAYER** (Role-Based Access Control)\nisAdmin.php  |  IsHeadteacher.php  |  isTeacher.php" as MW #FFF9C4

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' CONTROLLER LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**CONTROLLER LAYER** (Business Logic)\nAssignmentController | BookReviewController | ClassroomController | ExploreController\nHeadteacherController | LeaderboardController | ProgressController | ReadingController\nSessionController | SiteController | TeacherController | UserController | Controller" as CTRL #FFE0B2

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' MODEL LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**MODEL LAYER** (Eloquent ORM)\nBook | BookReview | Classroom | Genre | LeaderboardHistory | Phonic\nSchool | Student | StudentFavouriteBook | StudentReadingList | StudentWeeklyGoal | User" as MODELS #E1BEE7

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' DATABASE LAYER
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**DATABASE LAYER** (SQLite: <i>database.sqlite</i>)\n\n**Users & Auth:** users, sessions, password_reset_tokens\n**Schools & Classes:** schools, classrooms, classroom_student, archive_classrooms, announcements, hidden_announcements\n**Students & Goals:** students, student_streaks, student_weekly_goals, student_reading_lists, student_favourite_books\n**Books & Tracking:** books, book_reviews, book_review_upvotes, book_student, book_school_ban, book_school_stocks, book_genre, book_phonic\n**Reference:** genres, genre_student, phonics, leaderboard_histories\n**System:** migrations, cache, cache_locks, failed_jobs, job_batches, jobs" as DB #FFCDD2

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' CONSOLE / DB TOOLS
' ══════════════════════════════════════
rectangle "**ARTISAN COMMANDS, SEEDERS & FACTORIES**\n**Commands:** BackupBooks | FixBookData | FixBookGenres | ImportSchools | SyncBooks\n**Seeders:** DatabaseSeeder | SchoolSeeder | BookBackupSeeder | BookReviewSeeder | SyntheticSeeder\n**Factories:** UserFactory | StudentFactory" as CMD #D7CCC8

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' MAIN FLOW (Top → Bottom)
' ══════════════════════════════════════
PRES -[#1565C0,bold]down-> ROUTES : **1** HTTP Request
ROUTES -[#2E7D32,bold]down-> MW : **2** Route Matched
MW -[#F9A825,bold]down-> CTRL : **3** Auth Passed
CTRL -[#E65100,bold]down-> MODELS : **4** Query Data
MODELS -[#6A1B9A,bold]down-> DB : **5** Eloquent SQL

' ── Return flow ──
DB -[#B71C1C,dashed]up-> MODELS : Data returned
MODELS -[#6A1B9A,dashed]up-> CTRL : Model objects
CTRL -[#E65100,dashed]up-> PRES : **6** Blade View rendered

' ── Side connections ──
CMD -[#5D4037,dotted]up-> DB : Modifies & Seeds\nDatabase directly

' ══════════════════════════════════════
' LEGEND
' ══════════════════════════════════════
legend bottom right
  |= Colour |= Layer |
  |<#B3E5FC> | Presentation (Views, CSS, Assets) |
  |<#C8E6C9> | Routing |
  |<#FFF9C4> | Middleware (Auth & Role Checks) |
  |<#FFE0B2> | Controllers (Business Logic) |
  |<#E1BEE7> | Models (Eloquent ORM) |
  |<#FFCDD2> | Database (SQLite: 32 Tables) |
  |<#D7CCC8> | CLI Commands, Seeders & Factories |
end legend

@enduml